imdb.plot outline: A countdown of superlatives: the top 10 highlights from a particular area of the charged world of Red Bull. It's a true Pandora's box of action, excitement and extreme sport, out of which comes one surprise after the next: for example, the Colombian cliff-jumping legend Orlando Duque and many other stars in this sport. From topics such as "the fastest of all sports", "the most incredible free falls", "the most spectacular ground-breakers", "the most exciting world records", to "the most daring things you've ever seen in winter sport", Red Bull Tops brings you top entertainment which is guaranteed to provide a thrill.
